{"tid":2442440,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"B站關聯公司新增「金坷垃」商標申請信息","createTime":"2021-03-11T10:56:35.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-11T14:30:46.000Z","uid":73381,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"f5581ed58c81fd4f7f7eca6d8414003fbec98fdb","tid":2442440,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T10:56:35.000Z","msg":"內地線上娛樂平台嗶哩嗶哩（Bilibili、B站，美：BILI）預計第一季回港第二上市。據內地傳媒報道，上海嗶哩嗶哩科技有限公司入股北京非凡大陸文化傳媒有限公司，持有非凡大陸約20%股權。嗶哩嗶哩股價現升近7%，報129.8美元。<br />\n<br />\n北京非凡大陸文化傳媒有限公司成立於2014年1月，經營範圍包括組織文化藝術交流活動、電腦動畫設計、影視策劃、承辦展覽展示活動以及會議服務。另外，<span class=\"red\">B站關聯公司上海幻電信息科技有限公司新增「金坷垃」商標申請信息，申請日期為2021年1月25日</span>，國際分類為科學儀器，商標狀態顯示為「商標申請中」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/AXWypFP1bJE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FAXWypFP1bJE&d=XsjoyflP4JPXBkuZaWCkHcdEKmWGZzYthIwftZf8Bt0%3D&h=6679d635\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/AXWypFP1bJE</a><br />\n<strong><em><span class=\"xx-large\"><br />\n金坷垃強勢回歸  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></em></strong>"},{"pid":"22bb0384220f92cf050d3313dcd4cf88298ddfe8","tid":2442440,"uid":388757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T10:57:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f679aa72fdbb80c908a282c3eb0cb40c12d5e97","tid":2442440,"uid":73381,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"22bb0384220f92cf050d3313dcd4cf88298ddfe8","tid":2442440,"uid":388757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T10:57:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T10:58:12.000Z","msg":"點能樣？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d99f99ad2889f20f7b33503b3b96db7a58ddd521","tid":2442440,"uid":37966